---
title: "applyAllowlistedReceiverUpdates (FeeAggregator)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_remove_loop: process removals
    q_remove_loop --> q_remove_recv: for each (chainSelector, receivers) to remove
    q_remove_recv --> q_remove_inner: for each receiver
    q_remove_inner --> q_error_not_found: !s_allowlistedReceivers.remove(receiver)
    q_error_not_found --> [*]: revert ReceiverNotAllowlisted
    q_remove_inner --> q_remove_recv: removed successfully
    q_remove_recv --> q_check_empty_chain: all receivers removed for chain
    q_check_empty_chain --> q_remove_chain: no receivers left
    q_remove_chain --> q_remove_loop: s_allowlistedDestinationChains.remove(chainSelector)
    q_check_empty_chain --> q_remove_loop: receivers still exist
    q_remove_loop --> q_add_loop: removals done
    q_add_loop --> q_check_chain_zero: for each (chainSelector, receivers) to add
    q_check_chain_zero --> q_error_chain: chainSelector == 0
    q_error_chain --> [*]: revert InvalidChainSelector
    q_check_chain_zero --> q_add_inner: chainSelector != 0
    q_add_inner --> q_check_recv_zero: for each receiver
    q_check_recv_zero --> q_error_zero: empty or zero address
    q_error_zero --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroAddress
    q_check_recv_zero --> q_add_recv: valid receiver
    q_add_recv --> q_error_dup: already allowlisted
    q_error_dup --> [*]: revert ReceiverAlreadyAllowlisted
    q_add_recv --> q_add_inner: added successfully
    q_add_inner --> q_add_chain: add chain to allowlist if new
    q_add_chain --> q_add_loop: continue
    q_add_loop --> [*]: all updates applied

    note right of q_add_recv
        INV-001: Destination chain auto-removed when last receiver is removed
        INV-002: Destination chain auto-added when first receiver is added
        INV-003: Zero chain selector and zero address receivers are rejected
        INV-004: Caller must have DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE, contract must not be paused
    end note
